msgstr ""

#: ../../source/scenic_quality.rst:203
msgid ""
"The visibility raster for a given structures viewpoint.  This raster has "
"pixel values of 0 (not visible), 1 (visible), or nodata (where the DEM is"
" nodata)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/scenic_quality.rst:205
msgid "**intermediate\\\\auxiliary_*.tif**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/scenic_quality.rst:207
msgid ""
"An intermediate raster created while calculating the viewshed for the "
"given structures viewpoint.  The values of this raster represent the "
"minimum height that the DEM must have in order for the terrain to be "
