"The calculated value of the viewshed amenity/disamenity given the "
"distances (in meters) of pixels from the structures viewpoint, the weight"
" of the viewpoint, the valuation function, and the *a* and *b* "
"coefficients.  The viewshed's value is only evaluated for visible pixels."
"  If an underlying DEM pixel is undefined (has a nodata value), so does "
"the valuation raster."
